==English==
===adjective===
'''rustproof'''

#Resistant to [[rust]], [[oxidation]] and [[corrosion]].
#:''This is is supposed to be a '''rustproof''' trashcan, but it can't handle the salt they use on our roads.''

===Verb===
'''rustproof'''

#To make resistant to [[rust]], such as by applying a coating.
#:''We'll '''rustproof''' the metal with a good coat of paint and then we'll be able to leave it outdorrs for years without damage.''